OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1783521458
OL,3,CPolitician resigns from committee with
OL,4,Cscathing statement
OL,6,FGuernsey Deputy Haley Camp has
OL,7,Fresigned from the island's Economic
OL,8,FDevelopment Committee with a scathing
OL,9,Fcritique of its leadership.
OL,11,FLed by Deputy Sasha Kasantseva-Miller,
OL,12,Fthe Committee which Deputy Camp was
OL,13,Felected to last year is "tasked to
OL,14,Fsecure prosperity through the
OL,15,Fgeneration of wealth", according to
OL,16,Fthe Government.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
