OL,3,CPolitician resigns from committee with
OL,4,Cscathing statement
OL,6,FDeputy Kasantseva-Miller has thanked
OL,7,FDeputy Camp for her contribution to
OL,8,Fthe Committee and says they remain
OL,9,Fopen to scrutiny.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
